 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usabbyfkb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sabbyFKB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 6:31:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1000 AC</span><hr size=1>  Get woven grass armor. THat is a trade for mana/hps over AC.<br>
